description:
Thrift Hunters, Season 1, Episode 1.

First aired on January 18, 2014.

Title: The Good, the Rad and the Ugly! (Pilot)

"Thrifting" experts Jason and Bryan shop secondhand stores in Las Vegas and Boulder City, Nev., in search of profitable items in the series premiere.

Shopping at thrift stores and antique malls in Las Vegas and Boulder City, Nev.; Jason finds a rare jacket from the cult 1986 film 'Rad'; bartering with the owner is a battle.

Format: x264, MP4.
